Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下該到極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村裏的守衛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和先生 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底是什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來需要增援了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了 上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是送給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是托尼卡村的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀 守衛的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 雖然被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像身負重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了些小事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很便宜哦 新鮮出爐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯吧 大豐收哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧我的技術高超呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑選魚餌的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒換魚餌之前一無所獲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜歡吃魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法茲 別太挑剔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃起來很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚腥味也大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽在的話 就能做別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在教室裏也哼過這首曲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裏的倖存者是希塞露的熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩提時曾一起生活過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直管他叫哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好久沒見過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到胖成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一點都沒變 我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他保護了五個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就開始了 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得肚子裏洶湧澎湃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個忍者護額的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是襲擊村子人的同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是什麼可疑的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 年久失修 請勿過橋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐 不行 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只能逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜 走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時性急弄錯了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們也差點因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露應該認識的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾在村裏擔任孩子們的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有勇氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭德和法茲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是小空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是雷歐的妹妹米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件背心不嫌大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這原本是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她非常喜歡 不肯脫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘寶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜為何想得到那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無頭緒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說那裏到底有些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經是名學者 研究過考古學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別對巨坑進行過相當縝密的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是關於巨坑的古文書的研究成果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據考證 這裏面記錄了某個歷史事件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上古之神創造的天之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被污穢之人奪去了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因污穢之人憎恨一切事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖利用那份力量毀滅世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股足以顛覆世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要將世界毀於一旦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個亡靈偶然撿到了力量的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化身為身覆赤炎者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向污穢之人復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過七度煉獄的激戰之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身覆赤炎者最終獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤炎者為防其他污穢之人玷污力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其分為七個音符並封印在這段音律裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是簡要的概括
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音律…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是兜偷的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果確實存在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天之矛到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為那是超越人類智慧的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實能感覺到那個巨坑中藏有什麼重大的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且不說盜取秘寶的惡行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連無辜的村民都趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事絕不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身有同感 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓兜償還所有的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家準備一起去泡露天溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小櫻混浴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是傳說中的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們進行修煉後 或許也能做到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人在這種鄉下地方也是名人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為是個相當強勢可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到既年輕又隨和 讓人大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個身體裏蘊藏著相當了不起的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一般大時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能救起一個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這道傷疤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前從懸崖下摔了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有50米高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好掛在樹上得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥反復叮囑我小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多克先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時他立刻抓住了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有一小時左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直抓著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不愛運動 缺乏腕力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很丟臉 很後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果希塞露死了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是哥哥的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭如此懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦成為了一名守衛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此付出了努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不太適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就各奔東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾去看他 總覺得有些尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就疏遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違的重聚 雖然很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有更強大的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更強…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥肯定很懊惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能救更多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了那麼多重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥 告訴我們訣竅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在我打算睡覺時發覺了村子的異常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間 村子便成了火海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被忍者襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我以為自己死定了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻突然停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同斷線的木偶一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穢土轉生這種忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以活人充當祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將死者的靈魂束縛其中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並強制將其喚醒的禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為只有第二代火影和大蛇丸會使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還不能百分之百成功地控制曉的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來忍術不夠成熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多克先生知道音律嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古文書提到的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來兜的目標是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關音律 您知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者有供參考的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上這個快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你把它扔在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但絕不可洩露此事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起 我們將和鎮裏的警衛隊合作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜尋那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有守衛被抓的先例
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會在您身邊安排護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那些得救的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上的福利院願意接收他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 這些孩子笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天夜裏以來 第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你設計的術式真夠亂來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不用趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你這麼覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸肯定會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用自己的查克拉改良了術式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定能成功控制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該試試擁有意識和記憶的狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些東西還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許被誰拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要讓我去找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初不是這麼決定的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很會使喚人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺越來越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,好孤單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,怎麼會寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,一直都在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,力量 第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,本月的幸運獎品是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,在明信片上注明必須事項和衣服的尺碼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,寄往所示地址
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,將抽選40名幸運觀眾發放獎品
